name: to become a little less full of shit
description: NFT of original 36x36 vibrant Cows painting. Still physically available as of 09/26/21. Painting was painted in 2020. Just like cows becoming less full of shit from all their eating, humans becoming less full of shit in 2020 and beyond may be an intention but for some and many, it seems the exact opposite. www.vibrantcows.com
